the more tedium you can remove from your life, the more awesome you can make. TextExpander, for me, is an awesome-enabler.\n\n\n\nWrap-up\n\n\n\nWe might have to schedule a call with David to chat about acquiring the rights to \u201cawesome-enabler\u201d for our new tagline. In the meantime, we thank him for offering some excellent insight into how TextExpander can be a great partner in the legal trade. You can find David on Twitter @MacSparky and pickup other productivity tips of his at his blog MacSparky.\n\n\n\nIf you have a story to tell, let us know. Keep up with our tips, and stories, on twitter @TextExpander or on LinkedIn.",
